---
title: Cal Smart Mexi-Cali Shrimp Bowls with Warm Bulgur Salad and Baja Sauce
description: Lightly-seasoned, pan-fried shrimp shine in this balanced bowl featuring zesty bulgur, spinach and tomatoes! A liberal drizzle of Baja sauce over top is the best way to enjoy this delicious dish!
